 * - Multi-mode resolution (Platform, Density, Color Mode, etc.)
 * - Alias chains with circular reference detection
 * - Cross-JSON references
 * - CSS value conversion
 *
 * CRITICAL: All components must use this resolver. No hard values allowed.
 */

